name: Tigran Jamiro
Lore: 'Senior logistics officer from Onderon. Left Dantooine to serve on Yavin 4 before coming to Hoth. All personnel entering Echo Base must report to him.',
Text: 'Deploy only on Yavin 4 or Hoth, but may move elsewhere. Opponent''s aliens and Imperials may not move from same site as Tigran to an Echo or an interior Yavin site.',
